sentence: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Johnson & Johnson ( JNJ ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 0.6%.
Year to date, Johnson & Johnson registers a 6.6% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Home Depot ( HD ), trading down 2.2%.
Home Depot is showing a gain of 7.0% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Intel ( INTC ), trading down 2.2%, and Cisco Systems ( CSCO ), trading up 0.3% on the day.
